### ============================================================================
### UTIL-API-002 | 이메일 및 Slack 외부 공유
### Markdown source: docs/03_API/PHASE2_API_SPEC.md
### Endpoint: POST /api/gen/docs/{repo_id}/share
### 관련 기능 ID: DOCS-UTIL-B-202
### 상태: 시작 전 (Phase 2)
### 공통 오류 계약: ../_shared/ERROR-CONTRACT.http
### 보안: Slack Webhook URL은 응답·로그에서 마스킹하고 SSRF 방지 allowlist 적용.
### ============================================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = replace-me
@repoId = 3f7cc46e-d954-83ab-9f12-013b0c9d2a1e

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/gen/docs/{{repoId}}/share
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"channels":[{"type":"email","target":"newdev@example.com"},{"type":"slack","target":"https://hooks.slack.com/services/REPLACE/ME"}],"includeFullGuide":false}

### 200 OK
### {"code":200,"message":"success","data":{"sentChannels":[{"type":"email","target":"newdev@example.com"}],"failedChannels":[],"sentAt":"2026-06-18T10:00:00Z"}}

### [오류] 유효하지 않은 채널
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/gen/docs/{{repoId}}/share
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"channels":[{"type":"email","target":"not-an-email"}],"includeFullGuide":false}

### 400 INVALID_CHANNEL / 401 UNAUTHORIZED / 404 REPO_NOT_FOUND /
### 404 DOCS_NOT_FOUND / 500 SHARE_FAILED
